@NODE Story "The Story"
@{b}@{u}The Story of The Problem@{ub}@{uu}

This is were we will tell you all about how @{b}The Problem@{ub} emerged from
the dark corridors of @{"Aalten" LINK Aalten}

In 1992 there was need for a change!
The old computer house modules had become repetitive, so a new sound emerged
from the underground with as first example:

				@{b}The Problem

The Problem@{ub} first consisted of Alco "Rhythm" Lammers and William "DJ Infinity"
Westrum. Their work was and is not meant 4 public use.
In 1993 Thijs "Solution" Stalenhoef joined and since then,
they lost control!!!

Crazy as they are they are producing hi-quality modules at hyperspeed!!!
Nothing can stop them now!!!
@ENDNODE



@NODE People "The People"
@{b}@{u}The People of The Problem@{ub}@{uu}

