@NODE Companies "Companies"
@{b}@{u}The Companies of The Problem@{ub}@{uu}

The Problem have a few so-called companies. 

What are those companies?

Well... The part of @{b}The Problem@{ub} that composes music is now
officially renamed to @{b}The Problem Music Inc.@{ub}
This doesn't mean that the name has changed, it just indicates that this is
the Music Part of @{b}The Problem@{ub}.
Another part of @{b}The Problem@{ub} is @{b}The Problem Stories@{ub} wich
is responsable for the lovely @{"Wanda&CSilla" LINK Wanda&CSilla} story, and
ofcourse, this doc.

There are more of those company parts.
There is a @{b}The Problem Graphics Centre@{ub} that designs their own logos 
and pictures. Another is @{b}The Problem Programming Inc.@{ub}

Whatever happens : The original name '@{b}The Problem@{ub}' will not change!
@ENDNODE


