What you see here, is the start of an amazing adventure.
The story is a real thriller. Spooky scenes, nice soundeffects(?) and a
little bit of erotic stuff.
The story tells how @{b}The Problem@{ub} got in touch with Wanda and CSilla
and what happened after the first meeting.

You will receive a part of the story with every module you download.
Just collect them all, and find out what Wanda did to CSilla, what CSilla
did to Wanda and what @{"Bugles" LINK Bugles} can do to a human being...

Take a bag of Bugles and read all about the exciting lives of five persons:

	@{"Wanda      " LINK Wanda}
	@{"CSilla     " LINK CSilla}
	@{"AlcoRhythm " LINK Alco} 
	@{"Solution   " LINK Thijs}
	@{"DJ Infinity" LINK William}@{ub}

The story is written by @{b}The Problem Stories Inc.@{ub} and may not be
continued by anyone else!
@ENDNODE



@NODE Bugles "Bugles"
@{b}@{u}Bugles@{uu}

Bugles@{ub} are very crispy snacks, produced by a company called Smiths.
They are currently destroying their reputation (good reputation) by giving
@{g}Bugles@{ub} a new (stupid) name: @{b}@{u}3Ds@{uu}!!!

The Problem@{ub} is NOT happy with that, because they supported these
wonderful @{b}Bugles@{ub} in almost all of their modules.
Hell, they even named one of their modules after them...

All three members noticed that the taste of the (former) @{b}Bugles@{ub} is
slowly changing into something undefinable, that undoubtably Smiths are
calling @{"3D" LINK 3D}...
@ENDNODE



@NODE 3D "3D"
@{b}@{u}3D@{uu}@{ub}

What is (love) 3D...

The world in which we live has 3D dimensions. There are as many dimensions
in a world as you can imagine different lines standing under a 90 degree 
angle to eachother. When you....GET ON WITH IT!!! Said God to the writer,
and he did....
@ENDNODE



