@NODE Aalten "Aalten"
@{b}@{u}Aalten@{ub}@{uu}

Aalten is a little spot on the map. It lays slightly left of the utmost
corner of the world. To find it, just follow the marks (along the big
mountain) that say "Horizon" until you see a small road called
AaltenStreet. Go in there and you should find it! You can always ask
someone on your way, though not many people take this trip...
@ENDNODE



