@NODE Delusive "Delusive"
@{b}@{u}The Delusive Demo@{ub}@{uu}

What's this all about???

Well, this demo is going to be a major breakthrough in the demo-scene!!!
(That is, we HOPE so...) 
See it as a combination of a music disk and a trackmo...
Each mod will have it's own demo, their own unique set of FX!!!
Well...Here's sumtin about these modules...

Nota Bene: All these modules combined form @{b}The Problem@{ub}s FIRST ever EP!!!
           They call it 'The Synchronized Minds EP'.....Get that demo now!
	   
@{b}1. Synchronized minds
The Problem@{ub} seems to have synchronized minds...Always when they are
together, they will say the same things at the same time, and do the same
doings at the same interval :-)).
What about the track then? Well...Breakbeats...Acid Bleeps...Ruff synths!!!
Warp-Factor 9!!!

@{b}2. Floating Sheep@{ub}
A floating sheep is one free of pressure! A floating sheep is one at ease!
This mod contains (house :-) ) lots of 'twinkling' sounds, etnic drums,
there are no sheep, and they don't float! You @{b}WILL@{ub} after hearing
this fantastic module...

@{b}3. Long Term@{ub}
Making modules is a difficult process. You have to plan everything a long,
long time in advance. @{b}The Problem@{ub} have been planning a fast
brekbeat module for a long time, and this is it! 160 BPM, and reggae
backing. Hear for yourself...

4. @{"Bugles" LINK Bugles}
Well here is the @{b}The Problem@{ub} theme! They called it @{b}Bugles@{ub}
for obvious reasons. They live on them...
About the music: Its a @{"Mellow" LINK Mellow} track.
It's not entirely unlike a crossover between Country&Westerns 'Reincarnation'
and Slo Moshuns @{"'Bells Of NewYork'" LINK BellsOfNY} 
(No it's NOT!!! - Ed.)

@{b}5. Delusive@{ub}
....?
@ENDNODE



